headline: Stanley Black & Decker Announces Release Date for Fourth Quarter and Full Year 2025 Earnings
summary: Stanley Black & Decker (NYSE: SWK) will broadcast its fourth quarter and full year 2025 earnings webcast on Wednesday, February 4, 2026. The webcast will begin at 8:00AM ET.
